      "content": "That \"finding the right balance\" idea sounds a bit vague though. If you had to pick a side, wouldn't you say that prioritizing healthcare as a right is objectively more moral than prioritizing market competition and individual choice? Like, isn't one clearly more \"right\" than the other?",
